ium between perpetual and spot prices. The exchange uses an off-chain order book with on-chain settlement on its custom rollup, enabling sub-second order matching while maintaining decentralized custody. Funding payments are automatically settled between long and short positions, with rates typically ranging from -0.5% to +1.5% annually during normal market conditions."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
